description:
Collection of 300 unique Lunar Buddies trying to reach their Lunar base. Each Lunar Buddy has an unique set of different rarities and colors.

4 different head assets with the crown at only 10 % rarity
7 different backgrounds, with orange/purple at only 10% rarity
3 different coins on belt, with gold at only 10% rarity
7 different moons, with 2 color moon at only 10% rarity
4 different IOTA logo on helmet, with diamond at only 10% rarity
name: IOTA Lunar Buddies - First Wave
